---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner">
		<p>
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} GGGengXXX.
			<span data-locale="zh">用 Astro 和缓慢的注意力搭起来。</span>
			<span data-locale="en">Built with Astro and slow attention.</span>
		</p>
		<p>
			<span data-locale="zh">把零散的日常、笔记和实验先放进来，之后它会自己长出形状。</span>
			<span data-locale="en">Loose days, notes, and experiments can land here first; shape can arrive later.</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="social-links">
		<a href="https://github.com/GGGengXXX" target="_blank">
			<span class="sr-only">Go to GGGengXXX on GitHub</span>
			<svg
				viewBox="0 0 16 16"
				aria-hidden="true"
				width="32"
				height="32"
				astro-icon="social/github"
				><path
					fill="currentColor"
					d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.012 8.012 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"
				></path></svg
			>
		</a>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 3rem 1rem 5rem;
		background: var(--inverse);
		color: var(--inverse-muted);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.footer-inner {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-inner p {
		margin: 0.2rem 0;
	}
	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1em;
		margin-top: 1em;
	}
	.social-links a {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--inverse-muted);
	}
	.social-links a:hover {
		color: var(--inverse-text);
	}
</style>
